<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">IsZo</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Sometime before the 2008 financial cri=
sis,=C2=A0an investor named Brian Sheehy shorted the stock of a small bank =
called Capital Corp of the West, betting that it would go bankrupt. He was =
right.=C2=A0CCOW=C2=A0went extremely bankrupt, bankrupt enough that I can=
=E2=80=99t easily find a stock price chart. Here is the <a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25984731.270646/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjL=
mdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzEwMDQ3NDAvMDAwMDk1MDEyMzEwMDE0MjkwL2Y1NDk4=
OWU4dmsuaHRt/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB10fa8165" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" item=
scope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorat=
ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">final Form 8-K</a> =
that CCOW filed with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, noting th=
at CCOW liquidated in bankruptcy and its stock vanished in early 2010:</p><=
blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Company has concluded that beca=
use there are insufficient funds to pay all claims in full, common sharehol=
ders=E2=80=99 interests in the Debtor will be cancelled by the Plan and, ac=
cordingly, no distribution will be available for common shareholders. Pursu=
ant to Section 4.5 of the Second Amended Liquidation Plan, all of the Compa=
ny=E2=80=99s shares, warrants and stock options were cancelled as of the cl=
ose of business on February 4, 2010. Accordingly, the Company intends to fi=
le a Form 15 to terminate the Company=E2=80=99s registration under Section =
12(g) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"m=
argin: 16px 0;">Sheehy scored a win and moved on with his life. He started =
